#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Gilānavagga "
msgstr "2. Sick "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Nibbidāsutta "
msgstr "20. Disillusionment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.20:1.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the seven awakening factors, when developed and cultivated, lead solely to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn46.20:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.20:1.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.20:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These seven awakening factors, when developed and cultivated, lead solely to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.20:1.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.20:1.6"
msgid "Gilānavaggo dutiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.1"
msgid "Pāṇā sūriyūpamā dve, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.2"
msgid "gilānā apare tayo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.3"
msgid "Pāraṅgāmī viraddho ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.4"
msgid "ariyo nibbidāya cāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
